@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
scale 2

title Activity Diagram: Select Season, Race & Session

|User|
start
:Open the F1 Analysis Application;

|System|
:Display available seasons from FastF1 API;

|User|
:Select a season (year);

|System|
:Fetch list of races for the selected season;
:Display available races;

|User|
:Select a race (Grand Prix);

|System|
:Fetch list of sessions for the selected race;
:Display available sessions\n(Practice, Qualifying, Race);

|User|
:Select a session type;

|System|
if (Session data available?) then (yes)
  :Load session data from FastF1 API;
  :Display confirmation of loaded session;
else (no)
  :Display error message\n"Session data not available";
  stop
endif

stop

@enduml

' ============================================================
' ACTIVITY DIAGRAM TEXT DESCRIPTION
' ============================================================
' Use Case: Select Season, Race & Session
'
' Step 1: The User opens the F1 Analysis Application.
' Step 2: The System displays a list of available seasons
'         retrieved from the FastF1 API.
' Step 3: The User selects a season (year).
' Step 4: The System fetches the list of races for the
'         selected season and displays them.
' Step 5: The User selects a race (Grand Prix).
' Step 6: The System fetches available sessions for the
'         selected race (Practice, Qualifying, Race)
'         and displays them.
' Step 7: The User selects a session type.
' Step 8: The System checks if session data is available.
'         - If YES: Load session data from FastF1 API and
'           display a confirmation message.
'         - If NO: Display an error message indicating
'           the session data is not available.
' ============================================================
